originalText.text: Took child to see Dr. Trachtman due to blood in urine. Prior kidney specialist in NJ told me child had one of 4 possible life threatening kidney diseases and child needed to have kidney biopsy. Dr Trachtman got to the bottom of it, looked at urine under a microscope and determined the issue was actually coming from the GI tract. Child later diagnosed with celiac disease. Dr. Trachtman is a gem, extremely professional, super smart! So glad I got him for a second opinion!
